Variable Name 
=============
current_system_user -> the user of the Linux system that currently logged In


Funtion Name
============
system_user_read() -> Read user name and returning the username

Header File Name
================
user.h -> This will return current_system_user. system_user_read() is the funtion inside this header.

copyfiles.h -> This will do copy the file from internal drive and paste to destination drive

erase.h -> 
